      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>Your body rejects negative effects so violently that even your foes are disgusted.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Con 15</p><hr /><p><strong>Benefit:</strong> Once per day, when you succeed at a Fortitude save against an effect originating from an enemy, you can use a reaction to immediately projectile vomit as a ranged attack that targets EAC and has a range of 10 feet. This attack does not provoke attacks of opportunity. If you hit, the hit creature is @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.ZacF0l6IwqBwToTJ]{sickened} for [[/r 1d4]]{1d4 rounds}. This is a mind-affecting effect.</p>"
